response.overview: WSU Presents The 3rd Anniversary Event. March 6, 2010 The Biggest Womens Wrestling Show Ever on DVD. * WSU World Title Match One Year In The Making Special Referee: Molly Holly (c) Mercedes Martinez vs Rain * #1 Contenders Match To the WSU World Title Amber O'Neal vs Jazz * April Hunter vs Traci Brooks WSU Spirit Championship Match (c) Alicia vs Brittney Savage w/Rick Cataldo Three-Way Uncensored Match WSU Tag Champion Angel Orsini vs Amy Lee vs Sumie Sakai * Submission Match Jana vs Latasha * Dawn Marie Interview * Cindy Rogers vs Alere Little Feather * Alere Little Feather vs Rick Cataldo * The Boston Shore vs Tina San Antonio and Marti Belle * Angelina Love vs Sassy Stephanie This DVD features tons of backstage promos and exclusive commentary. Many fans are calling this the best womens wrestling show ever, and find out why today. This DVD is a special 2 disc release and features our best production yet
response.title: WSU 3rd Anniversary Show
